INSERT INTO `blog_entrada` VALUES (1,'se chingo el blog','2008-07-11 01:11:36','on midnight im update my django app blog, im do a backup called \"fixture\" on django, that is a dump a json data. and then load the data....\r\n\r\nim do some changes ... like delete some apps and make news apps... but when i load the data .. it\'s break!!!!\r\n\r\ni lost my datas for fool!\r\n\r\nNo problem restart again ....\r\n\r\ntoday im add myself to [foresight wiki membership][1] with the porpouse to be a member .. ok the meeting it\'s on 18 jul.\r\n\r\n[1]: \"https://wiki.foresightlinux.org/display/community/Request+Membership\"','se-chingo-el-blog'),(2,'comments-enable!','2008-08-13 09:02:05','Today im finished my comments app of my blog, it\'s called [zodycomments][zodycomments] and use [meteora widgets kit][meteora] for submit\'s forms.\r\n\r\n[Meteora][meteora] haves good stuff like dialog widget, forms widget... all this thinks im used on my work.\r\n\r\nOn foresight im add a [vnstat][vnstat] It\'s like a network transfer meter. With it we can know how many MB download over Inet.\r\nIm find this app, because i want a internet service called [BAM][bam] it gave internet conection for all places over cell network. On the service exist plan *limited* what you buy Mb for use. So i need know how many Mb consume my work. for pick the correct plan. And vnstat give it.\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code\"><pre>zodman@cosmogirl:~\r\n$ vnstat \r\nDatabase updated: Sat Jul 12 12:25:01 2008\r\n        wlan0\r\n\r\n           received:      64.70 MB (87.7%)\r\n        transmitted:       9.22 MB (12.3%)\r\n              total:      73.92 MB\r\n\r\n                        rx     |     tx     |  total\r\n        -----------------------+------------+-----------\r\n            today     64.70 MB |    9.22 MB |   73.92 MB\r\n        -----------------------+------------+-----------\r\n        estimated       123 MB |      17 MB |     140 MB\r\nzodman@cosmogirl:~\r\n$ vnstat  -u -iwlan0\r\nUnknown arg &quot;-iwlan0&quot;. Use --help for help.\r\nzodman@cosmogirl:~\r\n$ vnstat  -u -i wlan0\r\nzodman@cosmogirl:~\r\n$ vnstat  -d\r\n wlan0  /  daily\r\n    day         rx      |     tx      |  total\r\n------------------------+-------------+----------------------------------------\r\n   12.07.     67.43 MB  |    9.49 MB  |   76.92 MB   %%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%%:::\r\n------------------------+-------------+----------------------------------------\r\n estimated      128 MB  |      17 MB  |     145 MB</pre></div>\r\n\r\nThis is enable for foresight:\r\n\r\n          sudo conary update vnstat=zodyrepo.rpath.org@rpl:devel\r\n\r\n[meteora]: http://meteora.astrata.com.mx\r\n[zodycomments]: http://code.google.com/p/zodyblog\r\n[bam]: http://www.iusacell.com.mx/\r\n[vnstat]: humdi.net/vnstat/','comments-enable'),(3,'packaging the xfce-goodies','2008-07-15 05:25:15','im not very fan of xfce, its a great desktop! im know but im fan of gnome, well [Mark__T][1] package the xfce for foresight and i help with some xfce-goodies apps...\r\n\r\n\r\nall apps is enable on the [xfce rBO][2] a package some apps but not all!\r\n\r\nIf you want someone on foresight submit a [issue][3]\r\n\r\n[1]:http://marktmisc.blogspot.com/\r\n[2]:http://www.rpath.org/rbuilder/repos/xfce\r\n[3]:http://issues.foresightlinux.org','packaging-xfce-goodies'),(4,'conary-idea','2008-07-19 05:27:14','I have a small idea, forever when seen a app for package on foresight, im came to [rBO][1] site and search if someone packaged.\r\n\r\nSome equal it\'s:\r\n\r\n``conary rq  --labels --install-label zodyrepo.rpath.org@rpl:devel | grep -i <app> `` \r\n\r\nMy idea its make a python script what first download all packages, doing the conary rq to specific repositories, and get the  name with labels and save its on sqlite3 db. For then do querys for search package on db and not on [rBO][1]\r\n\r\nSomething like apt-cache search and apt-get update.\r\n\r\n[1]: http://www.rpath.com/rbuilder/','conary-idea'),(5,'newform on django Incompatible django from know','2008-07-21 04:56:38','Today im update the django-svn repo on this server and restart the httpd, DUD! IM BREAK DJANGO!!!!!!!!!!\r\n\r\nOh my Good, i have another [site](http://piccolinos.com.mx) here and it break too. GRrr and whats the problem ?¿ the new version of django have a newforms-admin implement and renamed and change alot!!\r\n\r\ncheck the [changes here](http://code.djangoproject.com/wiki/BackwardsIncompatibleChanges#Changedprepopulate_fromtobedefinedintheAdminclassnotdatabasefieldclasses)\r\n\r\ni have read the documentation again a learn again django...','newform-django-incompatible-django-know'),(6,'EL SUR GRITA','2008-07-21 05:06:02','[El sur grita](http://elsurgrita.com.mx)\r\n\r\n','el-sur-grita'),(7,'enli is coming','2008-07-22 23:42:42','[enli][1] is a great and the bigger Conferences about FS and LINUX. it call of papers to all linuxdud\'s of \r\nMexico....\r\n\r\nIt thinks the equal of linux expo conference (We have a linux expo but nothing similar of other contries).\r\n\r\n[Enli][1] is coming because they set a place ... [www.upaep.mx](www.upaep.mx) i seen it on [enli-twitter](http://twitter.com/enli/statuses/864303231)\r\n\r\ni want attend IT !!! great conferences\r\n\r\nhere a video on youtube of last year\r\n\r\n<object width=\"425\" height=\"344\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/MPZmff5tcNM&hl=en&fs=1\"></param><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\"></param><embed src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/MPZmff5tcNM&hl=en&fs=1\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" width=\"425\" height=\"344\"></embed></object>\r\n\r\n[1]: http://www.enli.org.mx','enli-coming'),(8,'Foresight 2.0.4 release','2008-07-24 07:21:31','Pues ya tenemos nueva version de foresight, mas bien no es una liberacion de nueva version,  sino  una actualizacion de la 2.0.3, esta actualizacion te instala la version mas nueva de gnome (segun lo [planeado][1]). Ademas de actualizaciones de muchos softwares como banshee y PackageKit.\r\n\r\nSi no hay nada nuevo ? aaaaaaaaah claro que si hay! tenemos CD nuevo, una version de 1 cd de gnome: [foresight lite edition][2], A diferencia de la edicion de gnome es que viene sin openoffice, y solo en ingles. Mas informacion en las [newsletter de julio][3].\r\n\r\nNo eh empaquetado ningun software nuevo en mi [repositorio](http://zodyrepo.rpath.org), lo unico que eh echo es actualizar el emesene y ya!\r\n\r\n\r\n[1]: http://live.gnome.org/TwoPointTwentythree\r\n[2]: http://www.foresightlinux.org/gnome-lite.html\r\n[3]: https://wiki.foresightlinux.org/display/newsletter/2008/07/23/Foresight+Newsletter%2C+Volume+2%2C+Issue+1+%28July+2008%29','foresight-204-release'),(9,'finde en merida','2008-07-29 05:49:36','Im very exited! estoy muy emocionado, Me acaba de confirmar el staff de vtauditiva, que estan organizando [\"el sur grita\"][2]. Que [FINDE][1] dara presentacion en MERIDA!! \r\n\r\nooooooooh DIossssss unas de mis bandas favoritas, las vere tocar en vivo!!!!!\r\n\r\nCreo que me entere un poco tarde!, No soy de revisar mucho myspace. AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAahhhhhhhhhhhhhhhh\r\n\r\nAlgunas bandas confirmadas que no aparecen en el sitio son: [natalia laforucade][3],  y genitallica\r\n\r\n\r\n[1]: http://www.myspace.com/finde\r\n[2]: http://www.elsurgrita.com.mx\r\n[4]: http://www.genitallica.com.mx','finde-en-merida'),(10,'now im a foresight member','2008-08-02 03:19:37','22:06 [freenode] -!- zodman n=zodman foresight/member/zodman You are now logged in. (id zodman, username n=zodman, hostname foresight/member/zodman)\r\n\r\nToday approve my membership to foresight team... and was accepted. [Pcutler][1] notice me.\r\n\r\nIm happy, i want help to this great foresight distro.\r\n\r\n[1]: http://www.silwenae.org/blog','now-im-foresight-member'),(11,'foresight feed','2008-08-15 00:28:57','Yeah in feed on foresight planet','foresight-feed'),(12,'zodman zone','2008-08-16 20:07:31','im remember a stupid action what i do on conferences of CONSOL.\r\n\r\nsomeone inmortal the moment.\r\n\r\n![zodman zone](http://www.tumamafuemia.org/imagenes/zodman_zone.jpg)\r\n\r\ntranslate:\r\n1pic: what happend if i put my home and swap partition on the same sector?\r\n3pic: noooooooooooo! what i do?','zodman-zone'),(13,'gwibber','2008-08-18 09:05:03','[gwibber][1] is a gtk app. What it use the social microblogging sites.\r\n\r\n![gwibber](http://img145.imageshack.us/img145/188/wibbercu1.png)\r\n\r\nIt have support for  Pownce, Twitter, facebook, Jaiku, Identica.\r\n\r\nThis is the only pownce client on gnome what i know. This is a good client for twitter, you can set the color for differences what services was posted.\r\n\r\nFor install:\r\n\r\n      sudo conary update gwibber=@fl:2-devel\r\n\r\n[1]:https://launchpad.net/gwibber/ \"gwibber site\"','gwibber'),(14,'RMS on merida yucatan mexico','2008-08-18 16:29:17','Richard Stallman comes to my city.\r\n\r\n> Richard M. Stallman visitará la ciudad de Mérida los días 24, 25,   \r\n> 26, 27 y 28 de septiembre y dará una conferencia titulada \"El software libre en la  ética y en\r\n> la práctica\" el día 26 de septiembre en el marco de las festividades por el\r\n> aniversario de la Facultad de Matemáticas.\r\n\r\nThis notice appers on the gusly users maillist its great. Im study on FMAT \r\n\r\n','rsm-merida-yucatan-mexico'),(15,'jira irc bot','2008-08-19 03:09:02','im working on [jira irc bot][1]. This bot is for work on foresight[,-devel} channel on freenode.\r\n\r\nThe objective is interactive with jira website without visit it.\r\n\r\nThe first step is maked. Make a page for suggest, wishlist and commands request.\r\n\r\nMy plans is build a python lib for interactive first with jira and then work on the bot. The bot can based on some excelents libs like [irc-lib][2] and a [repository of python bots][3].\r\n\r\nNow im doing a small script for do a shorts url. Im pick <http://te.tl> because is smaller than <http://tinyurl.com> and it not used alot. So it give us a very small url.\r\n\r\nI haved code small cli for make url on [te.tl](http://te.lt)\r\n\r\n    :::python\r\n    import urllib\r\n    import re\r\n    import sys\r\n    \r\n    \r\n    def makeurl( url ):\r\n        params = urllib.urlencode({\'url\':url,\'title\':\'\'})\r\n        f = urllib.urlopen(\"http://te.tl/index.php\",params)\r\n        response = f.read()\r\n        pattern = re.compile(\'<h1>.*</h1>\')\r\n        m = pattern.search(response)\r\n        if m:\r\n            html=  m.group()\r\n        else:\r\n            return \"Error: %s\" %response\r\n        return html.replace(\'<h1>\',\'\').replace(\'</h1>\',\'\')\r\n    print makeurl(sys.argv[1])\r\n\r\n\r\n[1]: https://wiki.foresightlinux.org/display/DEV/IRC+bot \"wiki irc bot\"\r\n[3]: http://code.google.com/p/ircbot-collection/\r\n[2]: http://python-irclib.sourceforge.net/','jira-irc-bot'),(16,'Check out all package on your branch','2008-08-19 16:07:15','I delete my repository/ directory on my conary dir where are allocade my packages. So i need all my packages again.\r\n\r\n    :::bash\r\n    conary rq --install-label zodyrepo.rpath.org@rpl:devel | grep -v \":\" |  sed s/\\=.*//g | xargs cvc co\r\n\r\nWith it i can check out all my packages on rpl:devel ...\r\n\r\nVery useful for me.\r\n','check-out-all-package-your-branch'),(17,'FL-1486 and Octuber Conferences','2008-08-20 19:31:08','Today i can fix a bug. [FL-1486](https://issues.foresightlinux.org/browse/FL-1486)\r\n\r\ni dont know why but this is the solution what haved on [gentoo](http://bugs.gentoo.org/show_bug.cgi?id=170630#c5)\r\n\r\nthe solucion is rename the Thunar desktop file\r\n\r\n    ::bash\r\n    $ sudo mv /usr/share/applications/Thunar-folder-handler.desktop /usr/share/applications/thunar-folder-handler.desktop \r\n\r\nAnd the gnome-open /home/zodman open the Nautilus.\r\n\r\nWell i will discuss it with [Mark__T](http://marktmisc.blogspot.com/) this bug and if that solve the bug.\r\n\r\nSo i will Attend to Two