s on [Foresight linux](http://www.foresightlinux.org)','pidgin-silc-support'),(50,'Adobe Air on Foresight','2008-10-08 18:44:14','Well im know adobe air as not the best tools of something, then for not exist stable version for non-{rpm,deb} distros\r\n\r\nSo with help of pscott i build a adobe-airc sdk for run adobe air on foresight\r\n\r\n`sudo conary update adobe-air=zodyrepo.rpath.org@rpl:devel`\r\n\r\nWell, the problem with sdk its slow, poor, and ugly. But works :)\r\n\r\n i can Update Pownce from it.  \r\n[![pownce](http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3233/2925769254_f45ee6c929_m.jpg)](http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3233/2925769254_09511dfe7a_o.png)\r\n\r\nwell tWhirl works too.  \r\n[![twhirl](http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2240/2924916965_c5c79bb0b6_m.jpg)](http://farm3.static.flickr.com/2240/2924916965_8e77b51be5_o.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nWell im read the twitter [ENLI](http://www.enli.org.mx) OMG the ENLI its FULL.\r\n\r\n<http://twitter.com/enli/statuses/952017167>\r\n\r\nThe last year comes around of 700 attends. This year i think comes arount 1000 attends!! \r\nWell this i can consider ENLI the biggets conferences of FLOSS on mexico.\r\n','adobe-air-foresight'),(51,'What packages its not on foresight installed ?','2008-10-09 14:16:48','Today someone on irc channel of #foresight on freenode ask for how search the packages what not are on official repo. Installed on her machine.\r\n\r\nHe forget that.\r\n\r\nSo do this.\r\n\r\n` conary q --labels | grep -v conary | grep -v foresight `\r\n\r\nOr search the packages what installed from a personal-repo\r\n\r\n` conary q --labels | grep personal-repo`','what-packages-its-not-foresight-installed'),(52,'foresight has OpenOffice 3.0','2008-10-13 16:42:35','Well yesterday (12 Oct) The openoffice 3.0 its enable on Foresight It\'s on 2-devel, so this mean  on devel label and for this needs report bugs.\r\n\r\n[![oo3.0](http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3252/2938806703_e9377c5453_m.jpg)](http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3252/2938806703_122a6652af_o.png)\r\n\r\nFor install it:  \r\n\r\n`sudo conary update {group-ooo-gnome,openoffice.org-base}=@fl:2-devel`','foresight-has-openoffice-30'),(53,'Small review of foresight mobile version [ESP]','2008-10-14 01:49:48','Im found this article, talking about foresight mobile edition on Acer Aspire One Machine:\r\n\r\n<http://blackshell.usebox.net/archivo/1198.php> on spanish.\r\n\r\nWe are not perfect. The Foresight Linux supported ( with full-hardware ) Classmate and EEEPC machines. my friend [Billy](http://billy.com.mx) say foresight mobile works on MSI Wind without problems.\r\n\r\nSo im want comment the thanks for talk about fl but comments are disabled on the post. Well tnx [Juan J Martinez](http://blackshell.usebox.net/)','small-review-foresight-mobile-version-esp'),(54,'Linux cluster on office gabinete','2008-10-16 00:49:39','<http://helmer.sfe.se/>\r\n\r\nHelmer its the name of this cluster. With video Render purpose. Interest History.','linux-cluster-office-gabinete'),(55,'im pass grade test','2008-10-17 15:39:18','[![examen](http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3216/2950283332_7f093ec650_m.jpg)](http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3216/2950283332_275b819e27_o.png)\r\n\r\nGlobal points: 1065\r\n\r\nWell with this im a graduate Computer Science engineer.','im-pass-grade-test'),(56,'Foresight release 2.0.5','2008-10-19 23:27:22','Bien dejemos un poco el ingles ( del cual es muy malo ). Este post es para anunciar\r\n\r\n<center>\r\n[![fl2.0.5](http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3053/2955435868_f7973e3199_o.jpg)](http://www.foresightlinux.org/gnome.html)\r\n</center>\r\n\r\nAlgo atrasado ... si!\r\n\r\nNo se habia echo el release de foresight linux por que teniamos muchos ISSUES sin resolver. Y hasta ahora se pudieron resolver. Sobre la fecha del release :) es la fecha que se hizo el commit del update no teniamos release para ese entonces. Gnome 2.24 se agrego oficialmente a la rama estable el 7 de Octubre.\r\n\r\n¿ Que trae foresight linux 2.0.5 ? [nota completa](http://www.foresightlinux.org/releases/2-0-5.html)\r\n\r\nGNOME 2.24  \r\n- Timer Track Applet  \r\n- Deskbar Applet  \r\n- Ekiga 3.0  \r\n- Nautilus con pestañas, ademas de que nueva vista de iconos ( control+F3 )  \r\n- [Mas notas de lo nuevo en gnome 2.24](http://library.gnome.org/misc/release-notes/2.24/)  \r\n\r\nApplicaciones  \r\n- OpenOffice 3.0   \r\n- Xorg 7.4  \r\n- Compiz 0.7.8  \r\n- PulseAudio 0.9.12  \r\n- PackageKit 0.3.4  \r\n\r\n** Notas, foresight 2.0.5 aun no integra empathy a la version gnome, seguimos utilizando Pidgin, debido a que aun no esta listo para substituirlo. Aunque esta disponible para su Descarga.   \r\n\r\n` sudo conary  update group-telepathy `\r\n\r\nEste mes es presentado Foresight linux a la comunidad de SL y OpenSource en las Conferencias del [ENLI](http://www.enli.org.mx) el dia 23 de Oct. a las 11 AM.\r\n\r\n','foresight-release-205'),(57,'the ENLI end.....','2008-11-01 01:48:28','Well im take my time to wrote this post... Because i have some stuff to do when i back from ENLI.\r\n\r\nNow ENLI  its the better an biggest Conferences of FreeSoftware and OpenSource on mexico. With 1k attendents, 6 talks/conferences on same Time, WOW!!!\r\n\r\nIm keep a foresight conference.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/zodman/2990679173/\" title=\"dscf0745.jpg por zodman, en Flickr\"><img src=\"http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3067/2990679173_6953951324.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" alt=\"dscf0745.jpg\" /></a>\r\n\r\nI have another 2 talks, about django & SMSGateway. the last  thats be very very funny because im forget a serial cable, for connect from my laptop to phone and someone get one. And Works! Yeah i can show the POC of the Conference.\r\n\r\nI can say \"Enli-Staff Rulz!!!!!!\"  \r\nTnx to mankod, stark, GeniusBoy( Master Chief), ZeoDove, Cerros, GPL. For all things to do for me!! that make me back the next Year. With another amazing Talks, ( This year i think the Hola-wey its the better what i have).\r\n\r\nOn it meet